asset.author: Keurig Inc
asset.hookText:
The Keurig Vue™ V700 Brewing System gives you total control to brew your way: stronger, bigger, hotter and with more choices than ever before. With a fully programmable color Touchscreen, strength and temperature control, 8 brew sizes, removable 74oz water reservoir, and revolutionary new Custom Brew Technology™ Vue™ ensures every beverage is brewed to perfection. Now you can fully customize your cup of coffee, tea, hot cocoa, iced beverage, specialty or café beverage to brew what you love, the way you love it -- every time!

For complete details visit keurig.com.
